  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can try and save someone who has died using the contents of a first aid kit. Attempt a @Check[type:medicine|dc:25] skill check on an adjacent creature that has died. If the creature died within 1 minute, the DC is 25. Increase the DC by 5 for each minute beyond the first. If successful, the creature is returned to life, at 0 hit points, and stable. The creature gains the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Yl48xTdMh3aeQYL2]{Wounded 2} condition. The DC increases by 1 for each time this check is failed. This has no effect on zombies.</p>",
